channel.title: Error_game_js5connect - How Do I Fix?
channel.description:
Hey all
Well first off, I have downloaded a 525 Client for my 525 server. But when I run the client, at, "Connected to update server" it gets this error in the cmd in the back, "error_game_js5connect." I seem to get this on about all the 508+ clients I try to run.
But I beleive I know the problem. I think the titan_cache may solve it. I don't have that and I can't find it. So if you know where to download that, could you please give me the link to download?
- Thanks!
